  <reg:acttitle>Motor Vehicle Act</reg:acttitle>
  <reg:title>Heavy Vehicle Diesel Emission Standards Regulation</reg:title>
  <bcl:ccollect value="statreg_vsis_solo"/>
  <reg:content>
    <bcl:section id="d2e27" toc="false">
      <bcl:marginalnote>Diesel emission standards</bcl:marginalnote>
      <bcl:num>1</bcl:num>
      <bcl:text>The prescribed diesel emission standard for the class of vehicle to which Division 40A of B.C.
        Reg. 26/58 applies is the allowable opacity in Column 2 of the following table set out
        opposite the applicable model year of the vehicle's engine under Column 1:</bcl:text>
      <bcl:centertext>
        <in:strong>Table</in:strong>
      </bcl:centertext>
      <oasis:table style="2">
        <oasis:tgroup cols="2">
          <oasis:colspec colname="c1" colnum="1" align="center" border="1"/>
          <oasis:colspec colname="c2" colnum="2" align="center" border="1"/>
          <oasis:thead>
            <oasis:trow>
              <oasis:entry colname="c1" align="center">
                <oasis:line>
                  <in:strong>COLUMN 1</in:strong>
                  <in:br/>
                  <in:em>(Model Year of Engine)</in:em>
                </oasis:line>
              </oasis:entry>
              <oasis:entry colname="c2" align="center">
                <oasis:line>
                  <in:strong>COLUMN 2</in:strong>
                  <in:br/>
                  <in:em>(Maximum Allowable Opacity)</in:em>
                </oasis:line>
              </oasis:entry>
            </oasis:trow>
          </oasis:thead>
          <oasis:tbody>
            <oasis:trow>
              <oasis:entry colname="c1">
                <oasis:line>pre-1991</oasis:line>
              </oasis:entry>
              <oasis:entry colname="c2" align="center">
                <oasis:line>55%</oasis:line>
              </oasis:entry>
            </oasis:trow>
            <oasis:trow>
              <oasis:entry colname="c1">
                <oasis:line>1991 and newer</oasis:line>
              </oasis:entry>
              <oasis:entry colname="c2" align="center">
                <oasis:line>40%</oasis:line>
              </oasis:entry>
            </oasis:trow>
          </oasis:tbody>
        </oasis:tgroup>
      </oasis:table>
    </bcl:section>
    <bcl:section id="d2e93">
      <bcl:marginalnote>Measuring opacity levels</bcl:marginalnote>
      <bcl:num>2</bcl:num>
      <bcl:subsection id="d2e101">
        <bcl:num>1</bcl:num>
        <bcl:text>The opacity levels described in column 2 of the table in section 1 are to
          be measured using the Society of Automotive Engineers (SAE) J1667 Snap-Acceleration
          Test.</bcl:text>
      </bcl:subsection>
      <bcl:subsection id="d2e110">
        <bcl:num>2</bcl:num>
        <bcl:text>The model year of a vehicle's engine referred to in section 1 is to be determined in
          accordance with paragraphs (a) to (c) in that order:</bcl:text>
        <bcl:paragraph id="d2e119">
          <bcl:num>a</bcl:num>
          <bcl:text>by the year indicated on the engine information label or on the vehicle
            emissions control label;</bcl:text>
        </bcl:paragraph>
        <bcl:paragraph id="d2e129">
          <bcl:num>b</bcl:num>
          <bcl:text>if there is no label as described in paragraph (a), by the year of the
            chassis as indicated on the manufacturer's statement of compliance label;</bcl:text>
        </bcl:paragraph>
        <bcl:paragraph id="d2e138">
          <bcl:num>c</bcl:num>
          <bcl:text>if there are no labels as described in paragraphs (a) and (b), the
            model year is to be considered pre-1991.</bcl:text>
        </bcl:paragraph>
      </bcl:subsection>
    </bcl:section>
    <reg:provisionsnote>[Provisions of the <bcl:link resource="leg" xlink:href="/legislation/96318_00" xlink:type="locator"><in:doc>Motor Vehicle
        Act</in:doc></bcl:link>, R.S.B.C. 1996, c. 318, relevant to the enactment of this
      regulation: section
        217]</reg:provisionsnote>
  </reg:content>
